.TH "diaglog" "1" "" "SequoiaDB User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH 名称
.PP
diaglog \- 新建一个 DiagLog 对象
.SH 语法
.PP
\f[B]var diaglog = new DiagLog( [hostname], [svcname] )\f[]
.PP
